<div class="row">
<div id="main" class="span12">
<div class="row new-base">
<div class="span4">
<div class="left-side">
<div class="page-header">
<h1>Welcome</h1>
</div>
<p>Welcome to the C.O.V. Module and Engineering Dashboard of the NSF STAR METRICS Portfolio Explorer. Please use the form to the right to log in. Upon log in, you will be redirected to the module/s associated with your account.</p>
<p>
<strong>COV Module:</strong>
This module is designed to provide C.O.V. members with new data to support the review of their assigned proposals and the overall division portfolio.
<br>
<strong>Engineering Dashboard:</strong>
Designed for Internal NSF users, this module provides unique views of division and program portfolios, including the Research Topics assigned to submitted proposals.
</p>
<p>These modules were developed as a collaboration between two Engineering divisions: Civil, Mechanical and Manufacturing Innovation (CMMI) and Chemical, Bioengineering, Environmental, and Transport Systems (CBET).</p>
</div>
</div>
